  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Let Kids Be Kids! Sports Day for Rohingya Children</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Peace Winds Japan will organize the &quot;Kids Be Kids!&quot; event which will be held on January 25 for the Rohingya refugee children attending the Child Learning Center in Camp 14, Hakimpara Refugee Camp in Bangladesh. 200 boys and girls (ages 8-12) will participate in sports activities to promote exercise, teamwork, and mental health. The harsh conditions of the camps often rob these kids of a bright childhood. This event is an opportunity to restore some of what has been taken!</narrative>
  </description>
